Hi @phamngocphu!

To reset the filters without postback, use the [`setFilters` method](https://mottie.github.io/tablesorter/docs/#function-setfilters).

Update the sort by modifying the [`sortList` option](https://mottie.github.io/tablesorter/docs/#sortlist).

Then use the [`pagerUpdate` method](https://mottie.github.io/tablesorter/docs/#pagerupdate).

```js
var $table = $('#my-table');
$.tablesorter.setFilters($table, [], false);
$table[0].config.options.sortList = [[1, 0], [2, 0]];
table.trigger('pagerUpdate');
```

