You can subclass `OAuth2Provider` and re-implement the `verify_request` method:

```python
class MyProvider(OAuth2Provider):
    def verify_request(self, scopes):
        scopes = expand_scopes(scopes):
        return super(MyProvider, self).verify_request(scopes)
```

